Farmer's boots are acquired from the Tithe Farm minigame in exchange for 50 points. They are a part of the farmer's outfit. The boots grant 0.2% bonus Farming experience while equipped.

The appearance of the farmer's boots changes when a player attempts to equip it after changing their gender via the Make-over mage.

This item can be stored in the armour case of a costume room.
